title: storybook-5-ch-2-par-1
transcription: ULara, ongubhantom, wayeyirhorho ekhethekileyo. Wayengafani tu nabahlobo bakhe, kuba yena wayenamaphiko akhazimlayo natyheli.

title: storybook-5-ch-3-par-2
transcription: Rhoqo kusasa, uBhibhi Bhabhathane wayebulisa uLara, kanti noManto Mntanezulu wayethanda ukumbulisa, ngokumwangawangisela.

title: storybook-5-ch-3-par-1
transcription: Wonke umntu wayewathanda amaphiko akhe atyheli.

title: storybook-5-ch-4-par-1
transcription: Nkqu noSesa Sigcawu onolunya kunene wayekuvuyela ukubona uLara.

title: storybook-5-ch-4-par-2
transcription: Esikolweni, uLara wayedlala nabahlobo bakhe abaninzi.

title: storybook-5-ch-5-par-1
transcription: Kodwa uLara wayefuna ukufana nabanye oobhantom. “Akwaba bendinamaphiko abomvu njengawe lo, Mama,” watsho elila.

title: storybook-5-ch-6-par-1
transcription: Ngenye imini, umama kaLara wapeyinta amaphiko akhe abomvu krwe, ngelizama ukumonwabisa.

title: storybook-5-ch-7-par-1
transcription: Ngentsasa elandelayo, akukho nomnye umntu owambulisayo uLara endleleni eya esikolweni.

title: storybook-5-ch-8-par-1
transcription: Akufika esikolweni, akukho namnye kubahlobo bakhe owamnika nomolo lo.

title: storybook-5-ch-9-par-2
transcription: Akho namnye owawaqaphelayo amaphiko akhe amatsha abomvu wade uNkosazana Miya wambona wathi, “Lara, uwapeyintile na amaphiko akho atyheli!”

title: storybook-5-ch-10-par-1
transcription: Oothuka kakhulu amaqabane kaLara. “Amaphiko akho atyheli akhethekile!”

title: storybook-5-ch-11-par-1
transcription: “Lara,” wakhwaza watsho uNkosazana Miya, “amaphiko akho atyheli ngawo akwenza ube ngulo mntu unguye – njengechokoza likaSipho nemilenze kaSally.”

title: storybook-5-ch-12-par-1
transcription: Akufika ekhaya uLara, wahlamba wayikhucula yonke loo peyinti kumaphiko akhe abengezela bugolide.

title: storybook-5-ch-12-par-2
transcription: “Soze ndiphinde ndiwapeyinte amaphiko am!” wacinga njalo. “Mhlawumbi ndakukwenza oko kanye okanye kabini ...”

title: storybook-5-ch-13-par-1
transcription: “...ndizame umbala omfusa ... okanye enye nje into entle. Kodwa ingabi yinto esisigxina, ibe yinto nje yokuzonbisa.”
